    "description": "{STEAM_APP_IMAGE}/extras/游戏介绍图.jpg<br><br>这是一款十分爽快的上帝视角射击游戏，玩家将扮演一名星际佣兵，探索贪婪大地这颗边境星球，拥抱“血腥大地（Crimsonland）+吸血鬼幸存者（Vampire Survivors）”的杀戮体验！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371540/extras/4117c682bfb81a01d2769f1b66452f07.poster.avif?t=1737700514\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371540/extras/4117c682bfb81a01d2769f1b66452f07.webm?t=1737700514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371540/extras/4117c682bfb81a01d2769f1b66452f07.mp4?t=1737700514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >直面潮水般的敌人</h2>在虚幻5引擎的加持下，《贪婪大地》的每一只怪物都有着精细的刻画，而且可以流畅运行成百上千蜂拥而来的怪物在枪炮下同屏，每一场战斗都是由血肉、钢铁、枪弹与能量组成的视觉盛宴。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371540/extras/a66f1a8336f74c18773676535c253691.poster.avif?t=1737700514\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371540/extras/a66f1a8336f74c18773676535c253691.webm?t=1737700514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371540/extras/a66f1a8336f74c18773676535c253691.mp4?t=1737700514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >打造你的超级战士</h2>《贪婪大地》含有坚实的肉鸽元素，通过不断解锁更多各种强力武器、技能，玩家可以实现许多强力的战斗combo，每一种都“突突突”的非常爽快，很有小时候玩“孤胆枪手”的感觉。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371540/extras/e987aac903b9c36734439830c6723ad4.poster.avif?t=1737700514\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371540/extras/e987aac903b9c36734439830c6723ad4.webm?t=1737700514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371540/extras/e987aac903b9c36734439830c6723ad4.mp4?t=1737700514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >丰富的武器库</h2>《贪婪大地》目前已为玩家提供了丰富的武器库，包含数十种主武器和副武器，以及众多功能独特的技能，为玩家提供近乎无限的可能，未来还会有强大的机甲可供操控！<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371540/extras/bc168dd6ebc761812146533c437dac1b.poster.avif?t=1737700514\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371540/extras/bc168dd6ebc761812146533c437dac1b.webm?t=1737700514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371540/extras/bc168dd6ebc761812146533c437dac1b.mp4?t=1737700514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >更多地图，更多敌人，更多玩法</h2>《贪婪大地》目前已提供了3张地图，多种难度选择，且每一张地图都有着独特的敌人组合，其中还包含着许多强力BOSS！<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371540/extras/fe4187f1ab44bc8825881ec9ed9997b4.poster.avif?t=1737700514\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371540/extras/fe4187f1ab44bc8825881ec9ed9997b4.webm?t=1737700514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371540/extras/fe4187f1ab44bc8825881ec9ed9997b4.mp4?t=1737700514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>当然，游戏毕竟还处于EA阶段，将来会有更多的新内容，比如新地图，新的玩法模式，强力的新机甲，以及最多支持4人的合作模式等!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371540/extras/1add03a1a269a86be8b5ef0474870b2b.poster.avif?t=1737700514\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371540/extras/1add03a1a269a86be8b5ef0474870b2b.webm?t=1737700514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371540/extras/1add03a1a269a86be8b5ef0474870b2b.mp4?t=1737700514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>诸多新内容均会陆续更新，敬请期待！</strong>",
